Package: GRNSimilarity
Type: Package
Title: Single-Cell Gene Regulatory Network Similarity and Virtual Knockout
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Codex", family = "Assistant", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "codex@example.com")
)
Description: Tools for single-cell gene regulatory network (GRN) analysis,
    including GRN inference via hdWGCNA-like, ARACNE-like and SCENIC-like
    strategies, virtual transcription-factor knockout, network similarity
    comparison, and subgroup-based TF impact ranking.
